{"tid":2278611,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[調教我老母] 地方的老母需要黃色平台","createTime":"2020-11-09T09:22:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-10T04:02:10.000Z","uid":130904,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3ea261019503e803766b3aab130b400a3eac0244","tid":2278611,"uid":130904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T09:22:31.000Z","msg":"上文提要：<br />\n[屌我老母] 我個深黃老母話覺得攰喎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2278326\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2278326</a><br />\n<br />\n我老媽子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以之後我pass左表哥巴個幾個suggestion俾佢: 話左啦, 咪有囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我老媽子: 真係有人理你架原來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我: 咩叫&rdquo;原來&rdquo;同&rdquo;真係&rdquo;?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我老媽子: 無&hellip; 連扮靚同放假活動都有講, 好似都幾好喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我: 好咪得囉, 唔好阻住我打機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我老媽子: 唉, 係既, 你既點扮都唔靚, 放假又做毒男唔洗出街&hellip; 都唔關你事架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我: &hellip;屌我老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n_________________________________<br />\n<br />\nCr: J我啦表哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你老母需要嘅資料平台：<br />\n1. 雞蛋情報<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/eggies.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Feggies.hk&d=FEHxtXJUwAnPMx50BANU%2Bdey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=ce4cf7c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.instagram.com/eggies.hk</a><br />\n更新速度：每日一篇<br />\n內容：飲食/扮靚/市集活動/一日遊路線etc<br />\n<br />\n2. 港籽<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/gongzi.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fgongzi.hk&d=FEHxtXJUwAnPMx50BANU%2Bdey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=905a171a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.instagram.com/gongzi.hk</a><br />\n更新速度：慢（10月得1篇，9月7篇）<br />\n內容：工作坊/黃嘅品牌etc<br />\n<br />\n3. Timable<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/timable\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ftimable&d=FEHxtXJUwAnPMx50BANU%2Bdey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=f8798ed9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.instagram.com/timable</a><br />\n更新速度：平均每日2篇<br />\n內容：飲食/扮靚/市集活動/優惠etc<br />\n*但最近有幫7仔賣廣告<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家繼續俾貨，有再加"},{"pid":"5cc5f6564dbfb0b1923b9057470c7c4743ff1f1d","tid":2278611,"uid":130904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T09:23:42.000Z","msg":"有貨我再加呀 大家唔洗再睇新X期<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反正毒男係屋企無野做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97471831183825421039cf53c5d5cae3b62f4952","tid":2278611,"uid":130904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T09:24:40.000Z","msg":"你老母可能都好有需要<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59be322b95c1123f7d749b795f66471987f96232","tid":2278611,"uid":362284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cc5f6564dbfb0b1923b9057470c7c4743ff1f1d","tid":2278611,"uid":130904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T09:23:42.000Z","msg":"有貨我再加呀 大家唔洗再睇新X期<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反正毒男係屋企無野做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T09:25:36.000Z","msg":"買衫呢，毒男都要買衫買褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"424c82984c4dcc16ecfcf944230d4f3f1ce549e3","tid":2278611,"uid":130904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T09:25:38.000Z","msg":"唔係毒撚無人理掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" clas